      <title>即使在 WhatsApp 调查之后，银行仍难以监控员工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-05/banks-struggle-to-monitor-staffers-even-after-whatsapp-probes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管银行家因员工使用 WhatsApp 和其他未经授权的消息服务而被处以超过 20 亿美元的罚款，但华尔街仍在努力追踪银行家之间的各种沟通方式。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-05/banks-struggle-to-monitor-staffers-even-after-whatsapp-probes</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
